First we need you to authorize Tooddoc to access your Google Agenda calendars & events.

Click \"Authorize\" & follow the instructions.

Thanks you! You agendas will start to synchronize in a few minutes.

Don't forget that you won't be able to manually add or remove availabilities from Tooddoc. If you want to make yourself unavailable, add an event in your Google Agenda.

covid_notification:
Due to COVID-19, a ministerial order forces the compulsory closure of doctors' offices. Patients can therefore no longer make appointments with you via Tooddoc; they will only have access to your telephone number.

Only emergency services organised by professional associations are authorised. We will adapt the platform accordingly once they have been identified.
migration_notification: The old platform is no longer supported. We will therefore redirect you to this new, easier to use interface. You just have to register in the same way as before, your data has been migrated. If you forgot your password, enter your email then click on \"next\" and then \"connection problem\".
